'''Mark Zug''' is an artist who drew the cover for [[Star Wars Gamer 4|''Star Wars Gamer'' 4]] which featured the Starhoppers of [[Aduba-3/Legends|Aduba-3]]. He also drew the cover for the ''[[Star Wars: Dark Empire Third Edition]]'' trade paperback.

